cod
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:[The name of the Atlantic <i>Gadus</i>, transferred to various cod-like fishes of NZ waters, the simplex usu. preceded by a distinguishing (usu. colour) epithet: AND 1821.]
Origin:[none]
